OL,3,CBudget 2024: Do Tory claims of
OL,4,CLabour's 'broken promises' stack up?
OL,6,FOpposition leader Rishi Sunak has
OL,7,Faccused the Labour government of
OL,8,Fdelivering a Budget containing "broken
OL,9,Fpromise after broken promise", adding:
OL,10,F"Working people will pay the price."
OL,12,FIn his response to the Budget speech,
OL,13,Fthe outgoing Conservative leader
OL,14,Fclaimed Chancellor Rachel Reeves had
OL,15,Fdecided to "let borrowing rip" and
OL,16,Ftried to "cover up that splurge by
OL,17,Ffiddling the fiscal rules".
