OL,3,CBudget 2024: Do Tory claims of
OL,4,CLabour's 'broken promises' stack up?
OL,6,FFollowing the Budget, Sunak said:
OL,7,F"They said they wouldn't raise taxes
OL,8,Fon working people, they have. Broken
OL,9,Fpromise after broken promise and it is
OL,10,Fthe working people of this country
OL,11,Fthat will pay the price."
OL,13,FAhead of the General Election earlier
OL,14,Fthis year, Labour laid out it's
OL,15,Fmanifesto, assured it would protect
OL,16,Fworking people.
