OL,3,CBudget 2024: Do Tory claims of
OL,4,CLabour's 'broken promises' stack up?
OL,6,FIt said: "We will ensure taxes on
OL,7,Fworking people are kept as low as
OL,8,Fpossible. Labour will not increase
OL,9,Ftaxes on working people, which is why
OL,10,Fwe will not increase National
OL,11,FInsurance (NI), the basic, higher, or
OL,12,Fadditional rates of Income Tax, or
OL,13,FVAT."
OL,15,FIn the months that followed the Labour
OL,16,Fwin, speculation swirled surrounding
OL,17,Fthe ambiguity of the wording and
OL,18,Fwhether the pledge applied to both
OL,19,Femployee and employer NI contributions.
