OL,3,CBudget 2024: Do Tory claims of
OL,4,CLabour's 'broken promises' stack up?
OL,6,FThe Budget includes an increase in
OL,7,Femployers' NIC by 1.2 percentage
OL,8,Fpoints from April 2025, with Reeves
OL,9,Fsaying it is "the right choice to
OL,10,Fmake".
OL,12,FShe added: "And we will reduce the
OL,13,Fsecondary threshold - the level at
OL,14,Fwhich employers start paying national
OL,15,Finsurance on each employee's salary -
OL,16,Ffrom #9,100 per year to #5,000. This
OL,17,Fwill raise #25 billion per year by the
OL,18,Fend of the forecast period.
