OL,7,F"significant step" towards delivering
OL,8,Fon Labour's manifesto promise to
OL,9,Fintroduce a "genuine living wage for
OL,10,Fworking people".
OL,12,FThe increase, recommended by the Low
OL,13,FPay Commission, will mean an extra
OL,14,F#1,400 a year for a full-time worker
