OL,3,CBudget 2024: Do Tory claims of
OL,4,CLabour's 'broken promises' stack up?
OL,6,FIn addition to the hikes to employer
OL,7,FNIC, the Budget also set out rises to
OL,8,Fcapital gains tax (CGT), and a VAT
OL,9,Fapplication to private school fees,
OL,10,Fwhich Reeves said will help fund major
OL,11,Fcash injections for the NHS,
OL,12,Feducation, housing and transport.
OL,14,FHowever, in a bid to protect small
OL,15,Fbusinesses, she announced employment
OL,16,Fallowance will rise from #5,000 to
OL,17,F#10,500.
