OL,3,CBudget 2024: Do Tory claims of
OL,4,CLabour's 'broken promises' stack up?
OL,6,FHe told the Commons: "Britain's
OL,7,Fpoorest pensioners squeezed, welfare
OL,8,Fspending out of control and a streak
OL,9,Fof tax rises they promised the working
OL,10,Fpeople of this country they would not
OL,11,Fdo.
OL,13,FTo shouts of "up" from his own
OL,14,Fbenches, the former prime minister and
OL,15,Fchancellor said: "National insurance,
OL,16,Fup. Capital gains tax, up. Inheritance
OL,17,Ftax, up. Energy taxes, up. Business
OL,18,Frates, up. First-time buyer stamp
OL,19,Fduty, up. Pensions tax, up. They have
OL,20,Ffiddled the figures."
