OL,3,CBudget 2024: Do Tory claims of
OL,4,CLabour's 'broken promises' stack up?
OL,6,FLabour's manifesto previously pledged
OL,7,Fto reform workplace pensions to
OL,8,F"deliver better outcomes" for retirees
OL,9,Fand savers.
OL,11,FIn her Budget, Reeves reiterated the
OL,12,Fgovernment's commitment to the pension
OL,13,Ftriple lock, telling the Commons the
OL,14,Fbasic and new state pension will rise
OL,15,Fby 4.1% in 2025-26.
OL,17,FThe increase will see the weekly
OL,18,Fbenefit rise to #230.30 for the full
OL,19,Fnew flat-rate state pension.
