OL,7,Fremain frozen, an individual receiving
OL,8,Fjust the state pension will be taxed
OL,9,Fon their income from 2027.
OL,11,FThe Chancellor told the Commons: "The
OL,12,Fpension credit standard minimum
OL,13,Fguarantee will also rise by 4.1%, from
OL,14,Faround #11,400 per year to around
OL,15,F#11,850 for a single pensioner."
